In re Resignation of Banks.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Banks (1991), 57 Ohio St. 3d 609.]

(No. 90-2453 Submitted January 9, 1991 Decided January 16, 1991.)

The resignation of Charles D. Banks as an attorney is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
